The paper discusses the challenges and solutions for implementing massive MIMO systems in cellular networks, specifically focusing on the phase and amplitude instability due to RF impairments. This topic falls under the sub-categories of information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), systems and control (cs.SY), multimedia (cs.MM), and architecture (cs.AR).
